    "title": "京东规则动态一览（2025年5月12日-2025年5月16日）",
    "followRuleId": "1239415449385570304",
    "content": "<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则公示】</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1239485407964565504\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台店铺综合体验分规则》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">五星店铺认证其他特殊要求</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">调整。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1239906324435832832\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《关于粽子商品价格及包装管理的公告》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">对单价超过500元的盒装粽子实行重点监管，商家应当确保销售单价超过500元单品/盒装粽子的价格合理性。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1238011423397908480&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台发货管理规则》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">调整关于商家发货时效的要求，修订后，若商家承诺的发货时效&le;2天（当日、24h、48h），则要求商家在消费者完成支付的2天内完成发货即可。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">关联规则：</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1239414283402612736&amp;btype=12\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台个人个体交易管理规则》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1239487186232020992&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台发布违禁商品及信息管理规范-</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">刀枪实施细则》等实施细则</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">对违禁商品及信息管理规范增加实施细则，包括军警、野生动植物、未成年等。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1239751285499105280&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台商家套利细则》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">补充商家套利中的&ldquo;商家&rdquo;定义，包括商家加盟门店等关联机构。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">关联规则：【修订】</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1239751285499105280\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台商家违规管理总则》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">【规则生效】</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、【新增】</span><span style=\"color: black;\"><a style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: blue;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1238003186288168960\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台外置存储类目招商激励政策（2025.5.1-2025.12.31</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">主营京东开放平台外置存储类目的企业店新商家，若符合相关条件，可享受返还一定比例运营支持服务费。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、【修订】</span><span style=\"color: black;\"><a style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: blue;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1237218079084253184\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台店铺资质管理规范》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">明确商家关于资质文件真实性、合法性、准确性、有效性的相关责任。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、【修订】</span><span style=\"color: blue;\"><a style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: blue;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1237708714396487680\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台本地生活/</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">旅游出行/</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">到家服务/</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">二手回收类目资质标准》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">①将&ldquo;酒店预定&rdquo;调整为&ldquo;酒店预订&rdquo;；②增加国内酒店三级类目行业资质要求。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、【新增】</span><span style=\"color: black;\"><a style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: blue;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1236920694848229376&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台安心品质鞋靴商品认证标准》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">对材质、性能、功能分级等推优标准进行细化。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">关联规则：【新增】</span><span style=\"color: black;\"><a style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: blue;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetailNew.action?ruleId=1236922714049089536&amp;btype=2\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东自营安心品质休闲鞋商品认证标准》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、【新增】</span><span style=\"color: blue;\"><a style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: blue;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1237975736313319424&amp;btype=14\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《2025</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">年京东开放平台心动购物季活动总则》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">①活动节奏：预热时间：2025年05月13日00:00:00-2025年05月13日19:59:59，活动时间：2025年05月13日20:00:00-2025年05月28日23:59:59；②活动玩法：送礼专享折扣、官方立减、平台满200元减20元神券、跨店满减、商品打标。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、【新增】</span><span style=\"color: blue;\"><a style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: blue;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1237974540026515456&amp;btype=14\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《2025</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">年京东开放平台心动购物季送礼专享折扣活动规则》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">本次京东心动购物季主推送礼专享折扣85折促销，促销生效期间，商家的同一款商品可全程参与，积极参与送礼专享折扣活动可更高效促进礼赠类商品的销售增长。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">7</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、【新增】</span><span style=\"color: blue;\"><a style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: blue;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1238011880363134976&amp;btype=14\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《2025</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">年京东开放平台心动购物季官方立减活动规则》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">官方立减是一种按类目设置折扣百分比的单品维度促销玩法，本次分为5%、10%、15%三档的优惠力度。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">8</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、【新增】</span><span style=\"color: blue;\"><a style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: blue;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1237973337951571968&amp;btype=14\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《2025</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">年京东开放平台心动购物季平台满200</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">元减20</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">元神券活动规则》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2025</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">年京东开放平台满200元减20元神券是本次心动购物季的促销玩法之一，是面向广大用户发放的专属神券。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">9</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、【新增】</span><span style=\"color: blue;\"><a style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: blue;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1237971627887693824&amp;btype=14\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《2025</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">年京东开放平台心动购物季跨店满减活动规则》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">本次京东心动购物季主推每满200元减30元的跨店满减力度，促销生效期间，商家的同一款商品可全程参与，重点鼓励全品类商家参与，并着重鼓励商家以全店商品形式报名。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">10</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、【新增】</span><span style=\"color: black;\"><a style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: blue;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1237969251839643648&amp;btype=14\"><span style=